EST PLAN
OpenCart Demo Website
1. Objective
To verify that the OpenCart demo website functions correctly by performing manual functional testing.
________________________________________
2. Scope
In Scope:
•	Login (invalid)
•	Product search
•	Add to cart
•	View cart
Out of Scope:
•	Payment gateway
•	Performance testing
________________________________________
3. Test Strategy
•	Testing Type: Manual Testing
•	Testing Level: System Testing
•	Testing Technique: Black Box Testing
________________________________________
4. Test Environment
•	OS: Windows 10
•	Browser: Google Chrome
•	Application URL: https://demo.opencart.com/
________________________________________
5. Entry & Exit Criteria
Entry Criteria
•	Website accessible
•	Test cases prepared
Exit Criteria
•	All test cases executed
•	No critical defects open
________________________________________
6. Test Deliverables
•	Test Plan
•	Test Cases
•	Bug Report
________________________________________
7. Tools Used
•	MS Excel
•	Chrome Browser
•	GitHub
________________________________________
8. Risks & Mitigation
Risk	Mitigation
Website down	Resume testing later
Time constraint	Test core features only
________________________________________
9. Approvals
This test plan is created for learning and resume purposes.

